Slowly a wide grin spead across the feline Maximals face and he sat up. 
He arched his back, the sounds of whirling gears and wire hummed around 
him as his frame contorted, coling in and out as he switched from beast 
mode to robot mode, standing shorter then Shadowcaster. User, it was 
great to see an old face back from the Matrix, even if he did go insane 
for awhile.

He grinned but the smile faded from the feral bot. He gave a slow nod 
of his head. "Yeah, but how are we going to do that? We can't just 
waltz in and say hey remember us?"

OMWOS
